Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:07.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:13.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:16.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:18.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
